"title": "4823: famine, physical",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4823",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A serious shortage of food caused by drought, war or natural disasters. Famine is seen as a sign of God's judgment on Israel.</p>\n<h2>Examples of famines</h2>\n<h3>In the days of Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">GEN 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1\">GEN 26:1</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of Joseph</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:53-Gen41:57\">GEN 41:53–41:57</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:11\">ACT 7:11</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of Ruth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:1\">RUT 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2SA 21:1</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of Elijah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1-1Kgs18:5\">1KI 18:1–18:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:25\">LUK 4:25</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of Elisha</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:38\">2KI 4:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of the prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:19\">ISA 51:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:13\">JER 44:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:15\">EZK 7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:10-Joel1:12\">JOL 1:10–1:12</a></p>\n<h3>In the days of Claudius</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">ACT 11:28</a></p>\n<h3>In the last days</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7\">MAT 24:7</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:8\">MRK 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:11\">LUK 21:11</a></p>\n<h2>Natural causes of famine</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22\">DEU 28:22</a> <em>crop disease</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1-1Kgs18:2\">1KI 18:1–18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:1-Jer14:62\">JER 14:1–14:62</a>KI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:24-Jer6:25\">6:24–6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:3\">2KI 25:1–25:3</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:4\">JOL 1:4</a> <em>locusts</em></p>\n<h2>Spiritual causes of famine</h2>\n<h3>The disobedience of God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:18\">DEU 28:15–28:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22-Deut28:24\">DEU 28:22–28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:38-Deut28:40\">DEU 28:38–28:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:42\">DEU 28:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:51\">DEU 28:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53\">DEU 28:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:24\">DEU 32:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:1-Judg6:5\">JDG 6:1–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2SA 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:13\">2SA 24:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:11-1Chr21:12\">1CH 21:11–21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:19-Isa51:20\">ISA 51:19–51:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:17\">JER 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:22\">JER 11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:11-Jer14:18\">JER 14:11–14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:21\">JER 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:17-Jer29:18\">JER 29:17–29:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:24\">JER 32:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:16-Ezek5:17\">EZK 5:16–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:11-Ezek6:12\">EZK 6:11–6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:13\">EZK 14:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment on the ungodly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:28-Gen41:30\">GEN 41:28–41:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:29-Isa14:30\">ISA 14:29–14:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:8\">REV 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:8\">REV 18:8</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of famine</h2>\n<h3>Desperation and death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:9\">LAM 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:13\">GEN 47:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:20\">GEN 47:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53\">DEU 28:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:3-2Kgs7:4\">2KI 7:3–7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:3\">NEH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:6\">JER 52:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:14-Luke15:16\">LUK 15:14–15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:28-Luke23:29\">LUK 23:28–23:29</a></p>\n<h3>God's people seek him and return to him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:6\">JDG 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2SA 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:17-Luke15:18\">LUK 15:17–15:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's provision in famine</h2>\n<h3>He gives warnings beforehand</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:25-Gen41:27\">GEN 41:25–41:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">1KI 17:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:1\">2KI 8:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">ACT 11:28</a></p>\n<h3>He gives wisdom to men</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:33-Gen41:36\">GEN 41:33–41:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:1-Gen42:2\">GEN 42:1–42:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:11\">GEN 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:4\">GEN 47:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:16-Ps105:22\">PSA 105:16–105:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:10-Acts7:11\">ACT 7:10–7:11</a></p>\n<h3>He provides for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:20\">JOB 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1-Gen26:3\">GEN 26:1–26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:2-1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:2–17:16</a> <em>Sometimes he provides miraculously</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:18-Ps33:19\">PSA 33:18–33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:19\">PSA 37:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:29\">EZK 34:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:29-Ezek36:30\">EZK 36:29–36:30</a></p>\n<h3>He sends deliverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1-2Kgs7:9\">2KI 7:1–7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16\">2KI 7:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:36-Jer32:37\">JER 32:36–32:37</a></p>\n<h2>Responses to famine</h2>\n<h3>Accepting God's chastisements</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:12-Jer27:13\">JER 27:12–27:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:2-Jer38:3\">JER 38:2–38:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:13-Jer42:17\">JER 42:13–42:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:27\">JER 44:27</a></p>\n<h3>Caring for one's family</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:11\">GEN 45:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:1\">RUT 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:1-2Kgs8:2\">2KI 8:1–8:2</a></p>\n<h3>Helping those in need</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:29–11:30</a></p>\n<h3>Praying</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:35-1Kgs8:40\">1KI 8:35–8:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:31\">2CH 6:26–6:31</a></p>\n<h3>Trusting in the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:37\">ROM 8:35–8:37</a></strong></p>",
